&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, February 15 (KCNA) -- A German preparatory committee for commemorating the Day of the Sun, February 16 and the 60th founding anniversary of the DPRK, Ethiopian, Venezuelan and Equatorial Guinean preparatory committees for commemorating the Day of the Sun and February 16 and Congolese and Thai preparatory committees for celebrating February 16 were formed with due ceremonies. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
